      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, so it's spotless inside and out. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new but at a much better price, this is definitely the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 43500.0,
